data.description: This 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home located on Mohawk St is ready for a new owner. Situated on a spacious double lot you have plenty of room to stretch out. The attached carport, large fenced in backyard and workshop with power make this home feel complete. Inside you have a  glass sunroom/entryway and large living room. It also has recessed lighting, hardwood floors and plantation shutters throughout. Washer, dryer and refrigerator to convey as well. New HVAC per seller. Call today to schedule your showing!
